Allow a search for different formats in a name [for example, Vijayalakshmi]
 A) 1) grep -e "VIJAYALAKSHMI" -e "VIJAYALAXMI" -e "VIJAYALKSMI" DETAILS.txt
 2) grep '[SH-S-X]' DETAILS.csv. 3) grep '[vV][kK]' DETAILS.csv ( for name and surname, exemplating: Vijayalakshmi Kumbar)
